# Commandline spec


#### Create site

olaf createsite site_name
	- creates config.py in the place

#### Olaf utils

olaf utils unix


`following command requires to be inside project site`

#### Run local server

olaf run
	- --theme
	- --port
	- --hostname

### Freeze as a static blog

olaf freeze folder_name
	- --theme

[by default freeze in current folder]

### Git uploader

olaf upload
	- --message
	- --branch

#### Github CNAME update

olaf CNAME domain_name

#### Posts create/delete utility

olaf create
	- --post
	- --page

#### Importer

olaf import file_name --type

#### Exporter

olaf export --type
